r non-institutional hospice), or \u2013 4. Unknown because patient \nmoved, or \u2013 UK. Other Unknown \n\nCoding Instructions \n\n\u2022  Code 0, No, if at discharge to a home setting, your agency did not provide the patient\u2019s current reconciled \n\nmedication list to the patient, family, and/or caregiver.", "type": "Document"}}